Rating: 4
I made this 2 weeks ago and it was so good! My hubby and I loved it and I am making tonight. I loved the tomatillo salsa and pickled onions, but didn't like the baja cream, it tasted too much like mayo. In the future I will just mix sour cream with a little lime to flavor it. Tonight I am trying it with tuna steaks b/c the mahi mahi didn't look that great at the store and I will try baking it instead of frying in oil. I hope it doesn't lose too much of the flavor, I will report back tomorrow! I highly rec. this dish.